	Dead plant material, biomass as dry weight [g/m**2] (Dead plant mat biom) * METHOD/DEVICE: Dried biomass sample * COMMENT: Measured on plot level
	Trifolium repens, biomass as dry weight [g/m**2] (T. repens biom) * METHOD/DEVICE: Dried biomass sample * COMMENT: Measured on species level
